om wearing silk or brocade, or sitting upon anything made from them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5499,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/swear-by-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15415,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Swear by Allah and tell the truth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSwear your oaths by Allah, be righteous, and tell the truth. Verily, Allah Almighty loves for oaths to be sworn by Him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 7\/267 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/not-swear-many-oaths\/","url_meta":{"origin":15415,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Do not swear many oaths for your business","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of swearing many oaths while trading. Verily, it helps trade but erases the blessing.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1607 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cIn this is the prohibition of swearing many oaths while trading,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14667,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/false-oaths-suicide-cursing-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":15415,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: False oaths, suicide, cursing, excommunication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Thabit ibn al-Dahhak reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears falsely by a religion other than Islam, he is what he has professed. Whoever kills himself with something, he will be punished with it in the fire of Hell. Cursing a believer is like killing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/prophet-oath-turner-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":15415,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: I swear by the turner of the hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The oath of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was, \u201cNo, by the turner of the hearts!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0628\u0650 6253 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15415","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15415"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15415\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15415"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadit